title: [P3D] RealAir - Turbine Duke v2
description:
RealAir - Turbine Duke v2

[Latest Dual installer for P3Dv2 / P3Dv3]

Thanks to our good old friend leopard87 for providing the source files

--
This is a custom installer for RealAir Simulations Turbine Duke V2.

P3D v2 and P3D v3 versions of Turbine Duke V2 are included in this installer.

Please uninstall ANY other version of Turbine Duke V2 installed in P3D on your computer BEFORE installing this package.

The installer includes the following changes over the original Turbine Duke V2 P3D packages:

- Minor fixes to the sound package to eliminate the mild sound phasing problem.
- Minor fixes to the packages to prevent possible problems with the custom XML sound system
